data.title: Fast Dining in the Hood...
data.text: In spite of the fact that this is a busy location, they work quickly to get you in and get you out. Other McDonalds' locations that I've visited, they've only had one cash register open and the line was super long. At this location, they work fast. And of course, the prices are good. The location itself is located in the hood, but this is not the fault of McDonalds.

data.title: clean and convient
data.text: Easy in and out Staff friendly  newly redecorated McDonalds.  TV's for the early news on.  Comfortable.  Good in and out access
